# napi build artifacts (the native addon + the generated JS loader/types) and npm install state.
# Regenerated by `napi build` / `npm install`; produced fresh in CI and at publish time.
*.node
/index.js
/index.d.ts
/node_modules
/npm

# Files scripts/assemble-npm.mjs copies in at publish time: the wasm-pack web build
# (the `./wasm` export) and the repo README/LICENSE npm auto-includes in the tarball.
/wasm
/README.md
/LICENSE
